👉 Why use Runnable instead of Thread?
+---------------------------+-----------------------------+
| Runnable                  | Thread                      |
| ------------------------- | --------------------------- |
| Better design             | Less flexible               |
| Can extend another class  | Cannot extend another class |
| Separate task & execution | Mixed together              |
+---------------------------+-----------------------------+

